skills.name: Thwack
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Quantum DMG equal to 70% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Sheathed Blade
skills.simple_desc: Deals Quantum DMG to a single enemy and increases SPD.
skills.desc: Increases Seele's SPD by 25% for 2 turn(s) and deals Quantum DMG equal to 154% of Seele's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Butterfly Flurry
skills.simple_desc: Enters the buffed state and deals massive Quantum DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Seele enters the buffed state and deals Quantum DMG equal to 323% of her ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Resurgence
skills.desc:
Enters the buffed state upon defeating an enemy with Basic ATK, Skill, or Ultimate, and receives an extra turn. While in the buffed state, the DMG of Seele's attacks increases by 56% for 1 turn(s).
Enemies defeated in the extra turn provided by "Resurgence" will not trigger another "Resurgence."

skills.name: Phantom Illusion
skills.desc: After using her Technique, Seele gains Stealth for 20 second(s). While Stealth is active, Seele cannot be detected by enemies. And when entering battle by attacking enemies, Seele will immediately enter the buffed state.

relic_sets.name: Space Sealing Station
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's ATK by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's ATK increases by an extra 12%.

skills.name: Windrider Bullet
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Wind DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Deals Wind DMG equal to 70% of Bronya's ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Combat Redeployment
skills.simple_desc: Removes 1 debuff from a single ally, increases their DMG, and allows them to immediately take action.
skills.desc:
Dispels a debuff from a single ally, allows them to immediately take action, and increases their DMG by 46% for 1 turn(s).
When this Skill is used on Bronya herself, she cannot immediately take action again.

skills.name: The Belobog March
skills.simple_desc: Increases ATK and CRIT DMG of all allies.
skills.desc: Increases the ATK of all allies by 41%, and increases their CRIT DMG equal to 13.6% of Bronya's CRIT DMG plus 15.2% for 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Leading the Way
skills.desc: After using her Basic ATK, Bronya's next action will be Advanced Forward by 21%.

skills.name: Banner of Command
skills.desc: After using Bronya's Technique, at the start of the next battle, all allies' ATK increases by 15% for 2 turn(s).

relic_sets.name: Sprightly Vonwacq
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Energy Regeneration Rate by 5%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, the wearer's action is Advanced Forward by 40% immediately upon entering battle.

skills.name: Dislodged
skills.simple_desc: Deals minor Lightning DMG to a single enemy.
skills.desc: Tingyun deals Lightning DMG equal to 70% of her ATK to a single enemy.

skills.name: Soothing Melody
skills.simple_desc: Increases the ATK of a single ally and grants them Benediction.
skills.desc:
Grants a single ally with Benediction to increase their ATK by 32%, up to 18% of Tingyun's current ATK.
When the ally with Benediction attacks, they will deal Additional Lightning DMG equal to 26% of that ally's ATK for 1 time.
Benediction lasts for 3 turn(s) and is only effective on the most recent receiver of Tingyun's Skill.

skills.name: Amidst the Rejoicing Clouds
skills.simple_desc: Regenerates Energy for a single ally and increases their DMG dealt.
skills.desc: Regenerates 50 Energy for a single ally and increases the target's DMG by 28% for 2 turn(s).

skills.name: Violet Sparknado
skills.desc: When an enemy is attacked by Tingyun, the ally with Benediction immediately deals Additional Lightning DMG equal to 39% of that ally's ATK to the same enemy.

skills.name: Gentle Breeze
skills.desc: Tingyun immediately regenerates 50 Energy upon using her Technique.

relics.name: The Xianzhou Luofu's Ambrosial Arbor Vines

relic_sets.name: Fleet of the Ageless
relic_sets.desc: Increases the wearer's Max HP by 12%. When the wearer's SPD reaches 120 or higher, all allies' ATK increases by 8%.
